data.description: Nestled in a tranquil neighborhood corner lot in Alhambra, this exceptional 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom, 7,484 sq ft lot, 1,472 sq ft home embodies the essence of California living. As you step through the specially made Extended Oval Glass wood double front doors, you'll be greeted by an oversized window and a dining room perfect for hosting and gatherings. The kitchen boasts three extra-large windows, oakwood and pull-out cabinets, and a bay window over the sink, creating a bright and inviting space. Skylights and a pantry add to the charm.    The spacious living room features an oversized bay window and flows seamlessly into the oversized master bedroom with skylight, walk-in closet, and a private balcony. The ensuite bathroom is a spa-like retreat, boasting an oversized walk-in shower with a window. The master bedroom offers ample space that could be divided into two bedrooms, providing flexibility to meet your needs.    The guest room is equally inviting with wall-to-wall mirrored closet and studio lighting. The guest bathroom is a complete oasis with a separate bathtub and a walk-in shower adorned with decorative tiles. Tile floors run throughout the house, complementing the modern design.    Additional upgrades include a new garage door, rain gutters, driveway, patio, and fresh interior and exterior paint. The garage, equipped with all the necessary hookups, offers the potential to be transformed into an ADU, gym, studio, playroom, or any space you envision. A private automatic gate ensures security and privacy. The blocked wall backyard with privacy trees offers a secluded haven to bask in your most privacy. Close to shopping centers, gym, restaurants and easy access to the 710, 10 & 60 freeway. Approximately 9 miles to Downtown LA, 4 miles to Old Town Pasadena, walking distance to Fremont school. This is the California dream home you've been searching for!
